616
00:43:45,480 --> 00:43:46,400
But

617
00:43:47,719 --> 00:43:48,840
people say

618
00:43:49,599 --> 00:43:51,599
my dad just cares about money, even if it's wrong.

619
00:43:52,079 --> 00:43:53,039
Every line of work

620
00:43:53,320 --> 00:43:54,639
has people who are morally lacking.

621
00:43:55,320 --> 00:43:56,119
And the legal profession
is no exception.

622
00:43:58,400 --> 00:43:59,840
But if you really want to know

623
00:43:59,840 --> 00:44:00,639
