625
00:44:03,800 --> 00:44:05,000
Not just take their word for it.

626
00:44:05,679 --> 00:44:06,440
Right?

627
00:44:08,599 --> 00:44:09,920
If that's just gossip from people

628
00:44:09,960 --> 00:44:11,119
