I got over that ages ago.

637
00:44:35,800 --> 00:44:36,400
See?

638
00:44:38,360 --> 00:44:39,400
I'm even gonna write

639
00:44:39,800 --> 00:44:40,960
a little extra story about the main characters

640
00:44:40,960 --> 00:44:41,960
